## 1. Solution Overview

### Architecture

```
HR STAFF                   PIPELINE                        AGENT
────────                   ────────                        ─────

Upload document    ──▶    Validate file type
Fill 6 fields      ──▶    Check for scanned PDF
                          Detect duplicates
                          Generate AI description
                          Generate AI keywords
                          Confidence score check
                          Copy enriched doc         ──▶   Copilot Studio
                          to Library 2                    points ONLY at
                                                          Library 2

Change Status      ──▶    Status Sync Flow
in Library 1              removes doc from
(to anything              Library 2 immediately
other than
Published)
```

### Flow Summary

| Flow | Trigger | Purpose |
|------|---------|---------|
| Enrichment Pipeline | New file in Library 1 | Validate, enrich, publish to Library 2 |
| Status Sync | Item modified in Library 1 | Remove from Library 2 when status != Published |
| Review Reminder | Daily schedule | Notify document owner 30 days before review date |

